{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"DEPENDENCY ADDED (B5 fallout): B-RETIRE removes the bespoke run_review path, but PR #42 had to flip the DEFAULT gate_engine back to bespoke because the workflow PLAN-REVIEW verify/coach steps don't supply {{plan}}/findings on the live path (review-plan via workflow → INDETERMINATE). So bespoke is currently the ONLY working plan-review gate. B-RETIRE must NOT proceed until tepid-bus-pomp (0408) completes the workflow plan-review live plumbing + re-defaults to workflow. Otherwise retiring bespoke leaves NO working plan-review gate."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782505678304851001,"uuid":"0e731c26-03a7-4886-a38d-bd161d33dc19"}